###Option 1 - Launch via browser (recommended)

1. Follow the link: https://huggingface.co/spaces/mlproef/bspproject1-demo

2. Enter:
- Headline - news headline
- Text - text or brief description of the news
- Click Submit.

3. The system will analyze the text and generate a JSON structure with emotional reactions for different social groups.
(In this mode, you don't need your own API key â€” the model runs on my key, which is hidden.)
